B.Hu=s(["Cannon","Fork","Star","Arrow","Well","Crankshaft","Artillery","Racquet","Machine Gun Nest","Lobster","Watchmen","Sickle","Shooting Gallery","Airplane","Letter"],t.s)
B.H8=s(["Uncle Gena applauds. Ironically.","A sparrow lands on the gorod and chirps something sarcastic.","Somewhere, a babushka sighs at your technique.","The bat rolls away with quiet dignity."],t.s)
B.H6=s(['The bottle! Uncle Gena shakes his fist: "I was saving that for a SPECIAL occasion!"','Uncle Gena, tragically: "That kefir had sentimental value!"',"Uncle Gena stands up. Sits back down. Shakes fist in your general direction. He is running out of patience..."],t.s)
B.Gp=s(['The cauldron! Uncle Gena\'s ghost roars: "MY LAVA IS FOR SINNERS!"','Uncle Gena, aghast: "That lava took CENTURIES to properly curse!"',"Uncle Gena rises. Sits back down. Points a smoking finger at you. His patience: also cursed, also running out..."],t.s)
B.GA=s(['The martini! Uncle Gena gasps: "Do you have ANY idea how many olives that took?!"','Uncle Gena, wounded: "That was a PREMIUM vermouth!"',"Uncle Gena stands up. Sits back down. Adjusts his sunglasses menacingly. He is running out of patience..."],t.s)
B.H_=s(["The snowman lost his bucket. He is above such things.","The snowman is now a third shorter. The carrot remains optimistic.","Only a snow stump remains. It forgives you. Probably."],t.s)
B.GB=s(["THUMP. The snowdrift shudders. Something inside grumbles.","THUMP. A low growl rolls out from under the snow.","THUMP. The whole drift is shaking now. This seems unwise."],t.s)
B.is=new A.ds("en","\ud83c\uddec\ud83c\udde7","English",B.Hu,"Figure 1: {name}. Drag back from the player to aim!","New game! Figure 1: {name}.","A pigeon has requisitioned your bat for the flock. It offered no receipt.","Your bat is now modeling Uncle Tolya's finest underpants. The jury is impressed.","You hit the kennel! Barbos is escorting you off the premises. (+1 penalty throw)",'CRASH! A window! Baba Zina: "MY GERANIUMS! I know your mother!" (+1 penalty throw)',"That window was already broken. Now it's just rude.","THUD. The building remains unimpressed.","SPLASH. A nearby cat looks at you with centuries of disappointment.","First blood! You now throw from the half-kon (6.5 m).","The letter stays sealed! Knock out the STAMP (center pin) first \u2014 the corners walked back.","That was the LAST one! Uncle Gena grabs the broom and sweeps you off the field! (+1 penalty throw)","The pigeon grows impatient with your tactical pause...","Direct hit! The pigeon leaves a one-star review. You run off to wash up.","Freshly washed and ready to continue.","Right on the cap! You clutch your head, squat... and crawl off the field with what dignity remains.","A quadcopter has intercepted your bat! Estimated delivery: 3\u20135 business days.","A mole! It surfaced right in the gorod and redecorated your figure. It seems proud.","Figure cleared! Next: {name} ({n}/15){letter}"," \u2014 kon only, stamp first!","All 15 figures! Total: {n} throws. Even Barbos looks impressed.","Throws","Half-kon \xb7 6.5 m","Pull back & release!","Figure","All 15 figures cleared!","Total throws:",'The pigeons rate your performance: "coo".',"Play again","Sound effects",'8-bit "Akh, Samara-gorodok"',"Evening falls... Level 2: the evening yard! The wind is up, and somebody parked IN the court.","A gust of wind! The bat now has opinions of its own.",'CRUNCH-tinkle! The car alarm wails! An angry profile fills a window: "MY LADA!!"',"The alarm again. The whole yard hums along by now.","The owner bursts out of the entrance in slippers and chases you off the field! (+1 penalty throw)",'A resident of the manhole surfaces and catches your bat mid-flight. "Mine now," he explains.',"POP! The streetlamp is out. The yard is now 20% more mysterious.","BOING! The delivery robot spins on its wheels, headlights flaring, and speeds off the way it came.","A bat (the animal) has claimed your bat (the stick). Confusing for everyone involved.","The bat hangs upside down nearby, eyeing your nap with interest...","SPLAT! The bat leaves a droppings-based review of your napping technique. You run off to wash up.","A spider is spinning a truly ambitious web between the two lamps.","Caught in the spider's web! It really committed to that thing.","Select level","Level 1 \u2014 Daytime yard","Level 2 \u2014 Evening yard","Level 3 \u2014 Winter yard","Snow has fallen! Level 3: winter gorodki. The wind is fierce (40%!), the mole is asleep, and the crow is watching.","WHUMP! An avalanche slides off the roof \u2014 only your head sticks out! Level lost. Winter wins this round.","The crow stole a gorodok, inspected it, and dropped it somewhere else. Utterly unapologetic.","The crow has claimed your bat. She has plans for it.","The crow eyes your nap with growing interest...","SPLAT! The crow expresses her opinion of sleeping players. You run off to wash up.","The bat is stuck in the yolka! The star wobbles disapprovingly.","The frozen puddle! The bat glides like it never learned to stop.",'A skier carves past at full speed and snatches your bat off the ground. "MIIINE!"',"A blood moon rises... Level 4: Gorodki in a Nightmare! The pins are on fire, the wind is a brutal 80%, and something is watching from the portal.","Dawn breaks over the sand... Level 5: Gorodki on Vacation! The sea breeze catches every throw (100%!), and Uncle Gena is already working on his tan.","Level 4 \u2014 Nightmare yard","Level 5 \u2014 Beach yard","A sea breeze off the water! The bat drifts wherever it pleases.","You hit the grave! Cerberus climbs out of the portal and escorts you off the premises, all three heads barking. (+1 penalty throw)","You hit the sandcastle! An outraged crab pinches its way out and chases you off the beach. (+1 penalty throw)","That was the LAST one! Uncle Gena grabs his flip-flop and chases you off the beach! (+1 penalty throw)","Your bat is now hanging from a rusty chain, swinging ominously. Something giggles nearby.","BOING! The volleyball net is strung tight and springs the bat right back at you. A nearby team briefly applauds the form.","CRASH! That was no ordinary window \u2014 a dragon lived behind it, and it is significantly less amused than Baba Zina ever was. (+1 penalty throw)","The dragon eyes the broken frame. Still smoldering, still watching.","CRASH! You've hit the ice-cream kiosk. The vendor is unimpressed and charges you for a cone anyway. (+1 penalty throw)","The kiosk window was already cracked. The vendor shrugs.","The raven perches nearby, one red eye fixed on your nap with growing interest...","SPLAT! The raven delivers a distinctly supernatural verdict on your napping. You run off to wash up.","The seagull is circling. It has clearly done this before...","SPLAT! The seagull claims victory (and your sandwich). You run off to wash up.","A bony hand bursts from the grave and redecorates your figure with theatrical malice.",'A rogue beach ball rolls straight through the gorod, scattering your figure. Someone yells "SORRY!" from far away.',"The dragon breaks off from its circling, snatches your bat mid-air, and wheels away with it.","A seagull has claimed your bat for the flock. It has done this exact maneuver before.",'A paraglider swoops low and snags your bat mid-air! "Sorry, mate, thermal\'s calling!"',"THOCK! A coconut, dropped by that suspiciously tall palm tree, lands square on your head. You see stars, and possibly a lawyer.","The dragon leans out of the shattered window and breathes a jet of fire straight at you! You duck, cover, and reconsider several life choices.","You hit the trash bin! Two extremely startled cats launch out, backs arched, and vanish in opposite directions.","The snowdrift erupts! A very large brown bear climbs out and chases you off the field. (+1 penalty throw)","The ground splits open \u2014 THREE SKELETONS climb out, bones rattling, and shuffle you right off the field. (+1 penalty throw)","A monstrous spider descends from above on a thread of silk and wraps you head to toe in webbing. You are, for the moment, extremely stuck.","With a final heave, the silk gives way. Freedom \u2014 and several new personal fears.","Throws by level","The gorodki blocks stack themselves into a shuffling little figure, dance a few unsettling steps, and collapse back into formation.",B.H8,B.H6,B.Gp,B.GA,B.H_,B.GB)
